        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p>Hey {first_name, \"there\"},</p><p>Y'know, when I run workshops on newsletters, one of the things I emphasise is how important it is to maintain a regular schedule. And this is, for all but my American readers, a <em>very</em> late lunchbreak.&nbsp;</p><p>Ah, well. Do as I say, not as I doâ€¦ ðŸ˜‰</p><p>My feeble excuse us that I didn't manage to get it done before I had to prepare for a Audience Engagement and SEO masterclass for the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CivicJLab?s=20\">Civic Journalism Lab</a>. So, sorry for that.</p><p>Still, you can read it on your evening commuâ€¦</p><p>Uh, never mind.</p>"
      },
