      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "It appears that it's going to be an inherited system: if you managed to get your Facebook Page through the verification process to be registered as a News Page, people working for that organisation can get journalist verification.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "I'm not quite sure where that will leave freelancers, though. Given that they are the most vulnerable group of journalists, lacking the weight of a decent-sized publisher to back them up, that does seem like a serious oversight in a scheme whose stated purpose is to offer journalists more protectionâ€¦",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
